data.description: This charming home boasts three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a two-car attached garage with additional parking in the doublewide driveway. The beautiful engineered wood floors throughout create a warm and inviting atmosphere with high ceilings that enhance the sense of space. The kitchen is fully equipped with modern amenities, including a 4-burner gas range, microwave, and dishwasher, making cooking and entertaining a breeze. The master bedroom features a dreamy walk-in closet, offering ample storage. The master bathroom provides a luxurious experience with a shower and separate tub, perfect as your relaxing oasis. With its thoughtful design and well-appointed features, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style for delightful living. It won't last long, so schedule your showing today!
